",NA,2023-08-26,10,506473.83245198167,6080568.32925008,Yes,0.1,Yes,Yes,100,1.2,NA,1,NA,2.5,4.1,2.5,Yes,NA,Deep Fill,High,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,NA,1,3,1,5,"It appears as though this culvert is within a depositional zone, as substrate has been stretched out from the inlet and outlet areas. ",10,5,2,2,10,3,32,62," Expecting that, this would be a complicated and expensive fix to replace with an open bottom structure due to the need to raise the roads significantly.
